{"article_id":"FJxEgGDmllnv2HXf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Saturday promised supporters","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"that the wall on the southern border will be built ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"a day after he agreed to temporarily reopen the government for three weeks","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"without funding for a wall","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"-- but warned","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that \" both parties [ are ] very dug in . \"","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" 21 days goes very quickly .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Negotiations with Democrats will start immediately .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Will not be easy to make a deal ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"both parties very dug in , \"","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" The case for National Security has been greatly enhanced by what has been happening at the Border & through dialogue .","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"Trump signed a short-term spending bill Friday night","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"reopening the government ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"which has been partially shut down for 35 days in a fight over Trump ' s demand for $ 5.7 billion in funding for the border wall .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Democrats had balked at that number ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"instead offering $ 1.3 billion for more general border security .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Trump had announced","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that he would sign such a bill earlier Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"and Congress passed the measure hours later ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"sending it to Trump 's desk .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Trump said Friday","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"that he wanted negotiations for border security to continue ahead of the Feb. 15 deadline ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"and threatened to use the \" very powerful weapon \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"of declaring a national emergency","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"if negotiations came to naught .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"That move would give him extra powers","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"to build the wall via executive power .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"Trump has floated the idea of a national emergency before , something","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that would receive opposition from Democrats and some Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"But some Republicans backed Trump Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"noting","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"that he has agreed a week earlier to extensions of protections for illegal immigrants","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"who came to the country as children","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"and those from unsafe countries .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"ANN COULTER RIPS TRUMP OVER BORDER WALL ON BILL MAHER 'S SHOW","depth":3},{"id":36,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. , told Fox News Friday","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"that Trump had made concessions ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"and that","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"if Democrats won ' t negotiate","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"then Trump would be right to declare a national emergency .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"\" Here 's what I think","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"come February 15th ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"if the Democrats still say","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"' Go to hell on the wall","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"you get a dollar .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"That 's it. '","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"They basically tell Trump","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"' I 'm not going to do with you what I did with Bush and Obama '","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"then I hope","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"he will go the emergency route .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"We do n't need to shut the government down. \"","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"Trump has faced criticism from some conservatives","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"for backing down , for now , in the stalemate","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"and on Friday he responded","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"by saying","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that it was \" in no way a concession .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" \" It was taking care of millions of people","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"who were getting badly hurt by the Shutdown","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"with the understanding","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that in 21 days ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"if no deal is done ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"it ' s off to the races ! \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"he tweeted/","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"However , prospects for a deal looked bleak .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. said Friday","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that Democrats \" remain fully against a wall \"","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"but also said","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that Democrats would approach the negotiations in good faith .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"On Friday , Trump spent much of an address in a Rose Garden","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"talking about the dangers","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"that illegal immigration poses , namely the influx of drugs and criminals into the country .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"On Saturday morning , Trump was back to issuing those warnings , particularly about a caravan of migrants","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"heading toward the border .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" If we had a powerful Wall ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"they wouldn ' t even try to make the long and dangerous journey .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Build the Wall","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and Crime will Fall ! \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":114,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":100,"right":113,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":91,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":90,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":85,"right